<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Living Abroad Support | The Admission Architect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons|Material+Icons+Outlined" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style> body { padding-top: 0 !important; } </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="landing-hero" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.9), rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513635269975-59663e0ac1ad?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">Living in the UK</h1>
        <p>Your guide to costs, accommodation, and settling into your new home.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Understanding Your Living Costs</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Managing finances as an international student is crucial. The UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) requires you to have a specific amount of money to support yourself. Outside of London, you need approximately £1,023 per month, while in London, the requirement is £1,334 per month.
        </p>

        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <li style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
                <i class="material-icons" style="color: #1976D2; font-size: 30px;">house</i>
                <div><strong style="display: block; font-size: 16px;">Housing & Utilities</strong> Expect to spend £500 - £900 per month depending on university halls or private rent.</div>
            </li>
            <li style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
                <i class="material-icons" style="color: #4CAF50; font-size: 30px;">restaurant</i>
                <div><strong style="display: block; font-size: 16px;">Food & Groceries</strong> Around £150 - £250 per month if you cook at home.</div>
            </li>
            <li style="background: white; padding: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
                <i class="material-icons" style="color: #FF9800; font-size: 30px;">directions_bus</i>
                <div><strong style="display: block; font-size: 16px;">Transport & Daily Life</strong> £50 - £150 per month on buses, trains, and social activities.</div>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <div style="text-align: center; background: #E3F2FD; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid #1976D2;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976D2;">Need Help Finding a Place?</h2>
            <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 25px;">Finding secure student housing from overseas can be stressful. Let our experts handle it.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="calc-btn-primary" style="display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 15px 40px;">Sign in & Book Accommodation Advisor</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>